<detall><id label=""><![CDATA[66078]]></id><title label="Titol"><![CDATA[The father's dance at the Mercat de les Flors]]></title><excerpt label="Resum"><![CDATA[Vader reflects on the father figure and explores the time when memories turn into fantasies.]]></excerpt><content label="Contingut"><![CDATA[<p>Barcelona&#8217;s summer festival brings an international production, Vader, to the Mercat de les Flors.</p>
<p>Dance and theatre combine in a work that takes place in the visiting area of an old people&#8217;s home, in a place between the world of the living and the world of the dead, where the figure of the father stands out. The play unfolds in the broad territory between perception and reality, showing how time seems to slow down for elderly people.</p>
